# ArchMock Shared Types

All canonical types live in `packages/shared`:

- **Diagram**: `DiagramGraph`, `DiagramNode`, `DiagramEdge`, `DiagramZone`, `SDShapeType`, `SDProtocol` — from `@archmock/shared` or `packages/shared/src/types/diagram.ts`
- **WebSocket**: `ClientMessage`, `ServerMessage` — from `packages/shared/src/types/ws.ts`
- **Problem**: `SDProblem` — from `packages/shared/src/types/problem.ts`
- **Evaluation**: `Evaluation`, `DimensionScore` — from `packages/shared/src/types/evaluation.ts`
- **Session**: `Phase`, session-related types — from `packages/shared/src/types/session.ts`

**Rules**:
- Do NOT redefine these types in apps. Import from `@archmock/shared`.
- When extending, add to shared package and re-export.
- WebSocket handlers must validate incoming messages against the `ClientMessage` union.
- Diagram extraction must produce `DiagramGraph` matching the shared schema.
